## Preferences
- Be concise and direct
- Prefer modern best practices

## Agent vs Skill Precedence

**Agents take precedence over skills when both could apply.**

### Agent Rules
| Agent | When to Use |
|-------|-------------|
| `playwright-manager` | ANY Playwright/browser automation |
| `skills-manager` | Creating, editing, or organizing skills |

### Skill Rules
- Before starting any task, scan available skills for relevant matches
- Invoke skills via the `Skill` tool when the task matches
- Prefer skills over manual implementation

